data.description: Don't miss this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath, home on 5 acres in Sandia Park! This home has many recent updates including a new roof, baseboard heaters, garage door, and wood stove. The kitchen has been completely remodeled with all new cabinets and stainless-steel appliances and the bathrooms with refinished surrounds and new vanities. Enjoy care-free living with a new water heater and septic system upgrade. This home offers the feel of country living while also being close to amenities. Hurry, this home won't last long!
